\c 39
\s Nguvo tsvene
\p
\v 1 Zvino zveruvara rwedenga neruvara rwehute nezvitsvuku vakaita nguvo dzebasa kuita basa panzvimbo tsvene; uye vakaita nguvo tsvene dzaiva dzaAroni, Jehovha sezvaakange araira Mozisi.
\v 2 Wakaitawo efodhi \add ye\add*goridhe, ruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa.
\v 3 Vakapfurawo goridhe kuita mabape matete, ndokugura kuita twuwaya kubata paruvara rwedenga, neparuvara rwehute, nepazvitsvuku, nepamucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa, basa renyanzvi.
\v 4 Vakaiitira mapandi emafudzi akabatanidzwa; akabatanidzwa pamicheto yayo miviri.
\v 5 Nebhanhire reefodhi raiva pamusoro payo, raiva pariri; zvichienderana nebasa raro regoridhe, ruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\v 6 Vakagadzirawo mabwe eonikisi akaputirwa muzvikoshwa zvegoridhe, afomborwa sekufomborwa kwechidhindo, nemazita evana vaIsraeri.
\v 7 Zvino wakaaisa pamapandi emafudzi eefodhi, \add ave\add* mabwe echirangaridzo kuvana vaIsraeri, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 8 Wakaitawo hombodo yechipfuva, basa renyanzvi, sebasa reefodhi; \add re\add*goridhe, ruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa.
\v 9 Yaiva yakaenzana mativi mana; vakaita hombodo yechipfuva yakapetwa kaviri; kureba kwayo kuri chanza, neupamhi hwayo chanza, yakapetwa kaviri.
\v 10 Vakaisawo mairi misara mina yemabwe, musara wesadhio, topasi, nekabhunakeri. Ndiwo musara wekutanga.
\v 11 Nemusara wechipiri emaradhi, safiri, nedhaimani.
\v 12 Nemusara wechitatu haikindi, neagati, neametisi.
\v 13 Nemusara wechina bheriri, neonikisi, nejasipiri; zvakaputirwa muzvirukwa zvegoridhe mazvakaiswa.
\v 14 Nemabwe zvichienderana kumazita evana vaIsraeri, gumi nemaviri, zvichienderana kumazita avo; kufombora kwechidhindo, rimwe nerimwe nezita raro, mazita emarudzi gumi nemaviri.
\v 15 Nepahombodo yechipfuva vakaita maketani pamicheto, basa rakamonwa regoridhe rakazara.
\v 16 Vakaitawo zvirukwa zviviri zvegoridhe, zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe, ndokuisa zvindori zviviri pamicheto miviri yehombodo yechipfuva.
\v 17 Vakaisawo maketani maviri egoridhe akamonwa pazvindori zviviri pamicheto yehombodo yechipfuva.
\v 18 Nemiromo miviri yemaketani akamonwa maviri, vakaisa pazvirukwa zviviri ndokuzviisa pamapandi emafudzi eefodhi mberi kwayo.
\v 19 Vakaitawo zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe, vakaisa pamicheto miviri yehombodo yechipfuva pamupendero wayo kurutivi rweefodhi nechemukati.
\v 20 Vakaitawo zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe vakazviisa pamafudzi maviri eefodhi pazasi nechemberi kwayo, pakanangana nepakabatanidza payo, pamusoro pebhanhire reefodhi.
\v 21 Zvino vakasunganidza hombodo yechipfuva nezvindori zvayo pazvindori zveefodhi nerwonzi rweruvara rwedenga, kuti ruve pamusoro pebhanhire reefodhi, kuti hombodo yechipfuva irege kusununguka pabhanhire reefodhi, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 22 Wakaitawo jazi reefodhi, basa rakarukwa; rese \add re\add*ruvara rwedenga.
\v 23 Neburi rejazi pakati paro, seburi renguvo yeutare, mupendero wakapoteredza buri raro, kuti risabvaruka.
\v 24 Nepamipendero wejazi vakaita mapomegiranati zveruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute nezvitsvuku, zvakarukwa.
\v 25 Vakaitawo matare egoridhe rakazara; ndokuisa matare pakati pemapomegiranati pamupendero wejazi, kunhivi dzese, pakati pemapomegiranati,
\v 26 dare nepomegiranati, dare nepomegiranati, pamipendero yejazi kupoteredza, kushumiramo, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 27 Vakaitirawo Aroni nevanakomana vake nguvo refu nemucheka wakaisvonaka nebasa rakarukwa,
\v 28 nenguwani, mucheka wakaisvonaka, nenguwani dzakanaka \add dze\add*mucheka wakaisvonaka, nezvikadubura zvemukati \add zve\add*mucheka wakarukwa wakaisvonaka,
\v 29 nebhanhire, mucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa, neruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, basa remusoni, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 30 Vakaitawo hwendefa rekorona tsvene, goridhe rakazara, vakanyora pamusoro paro chinyorwa, sepakafombora pechidhindo \add vachiti\add*: UTSVENE KUNA JEHOVHA.
\v 31 Zvino vakasungira pariri rwonzi rweruvara rwedenga, kuti vasunganidze panguwani kumusoro, Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 32 Zvino basa rese retabhenakeri yetende rekusangana rakapera; vana vaIsraeri ndokuita zvichienderana nezvese Jehovha zvaakaraira Mozisi, vakaita saizvozvo.
\p
\v 33 Zvino vakauya netabhenakeri kuna Mozisi, tende, nenhumbi dzaro dzese, zvikorekedzo zvaro, mapuranga aro, mbariro dzaro, nembiru dzaro, nezvigadziko zvaro;
\v 34 nechifukidzo chematehwe amakondobwe akapendwa zvitsvuku, nechifukidzo chematehwe ezvikumba, nevheiri rechifukidzo;
\v 35 areka yechipupuriro, nezvibatiso zvayo, nechigaro chengoni;
\v 36 tafura, nhumbi dzayo dzese, nechingwa chekuratidza;
\v 37 chigadziko chemwenje chakazara, mwenje yacho, mwenje yekurongedzwa, nemidziyo yacho yese, nemafuta echivhenekeso;
\v 38 nearitari yegoridhe, nemafuta ekuzodza, nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuwhira zvinotapira, nechiremberedzwa chemukova wetende,
\v 39 aritari yendarira, nesefa yayo yendarira, zvibatiso zvayo, nemidziyo yayo yese, dhishi negumbo raro,
\v 40 zviremberedzwa zvechivanze, mbiru dzazvo, nezvigadziko zvadzo, nechiremberedzwa chesuwo rechivanze, rwonzi rwacho, nehoko dzacho, nemidziyo yese yebasa retabhenakeri, retende rekusangana;
\v 41 nguvo dzebasa dzekushanda panzvimbo tsvene, nenguvo tsvene dzaAroni mupristi, nenguvo dzevanakomana vake, kuti vashumira paupristi.
\v 42 Maererano kuzvese Jehovha zvaakaraira Mozisi, saizvozvo vana vaIsraeri vakaita basa rese.
\v 43 Zvino Mozisi wakatarisa basa rese, zvino tarira, vakange variita Jehovha sezvaakange avaraira, saizvozvowo vakariita; Mozisi ndokuvaropafadza.